<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <style>
            .container {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            }
            .header {
                background-color: #dc3545;
                color: white;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px;
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
                border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
            }
            .warning-icon {
                font-size: 48px;
                text-align: center;
                color: #dc3545;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            .reason {
                background-color: #fff;
                padding: 15px;
                border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            .support {
                background-color: #e9ecef;
                padding: 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Account Suspended</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="warning-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
                <p>Dear <%= username%>,</p>
                <p>
                    Your account has been temporarily suspended due to multiple violations of our Community Guidelines.
                </p>

                <div class="reason">
                    <strong>Reason for suspension:</strong>
                    <p>Multiple reports of inappropriate comments that violate our community standards.</p>
                    <strong>Duration:</strong>
                    <% if (duration === 'permanent') { %>
                    <p>Your account has been permanently suspended.</p>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <p>Your account has been: <%= duration %></p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <p>During this period, you will not be able to log into our website</p>

                <div class="support">
                    <p>
                        If you believe this is a mistake or would like to appeal this decision, please contact our
                        support team at:
                    </p>
                    <p>üìß <a href="mailto:npbloc.cntt@gmail.com">npbloc.cntt@gmail.com</a></p>
                </div>

                <p>We encourage you to review our Community Guidelines to prevent future violations.</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br />The Melodies Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
